overview: Work all day, work all night, there’s never a moment for our beauties to leave the office these days, but even the most professional of Private babes will find time to get down! The stunning Candee Licious wastes no time seducing a new employee for some afternoon entertainment, meanwhile Shrima Malati takes full advantage of a coffee break by getting some milk from her partner. Candice Luciana is also determined to show her boss that she can be much more than just an assistant, and Ivi Rein sure knows how to seal the deal after a long meeting! Private Movies, What Happens in the Office, it’s time to get to work!
title: What Happens in the Office...
